      "description": "Aplós employs a sophisticated, restrained aesthetic, balancing dark elegance with a warm, clean light theme for content. Stark monochrome primary surfaces create a high-contrast foundation. Typography is refined and understated, while interactive elements are subtly defined by borders rather than heavy fills. The system favors spacious layouts and soft transitions, suggesting a premium, calm, and deliberate user experience.",
